rday\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 355}, {\"ngram\": \"the Kimana\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 378}, {\"ngram\": \"some 200km\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"120 miles\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 426}, {\"ngram\": \"160 athletes\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"40 young women\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 485}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The young people were taking part in a reinterpretation of the \\\"Olamayio\\\" rites undertaken by young Maasai men to prove their skills, identify their leaders and attract girlfriends.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 3.2873081669424496e-13, \"text\": \"Maasai\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maasai_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The young people\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 540, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"a reinterpretation\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 566}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Olamayio\\\" rites\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"their skills\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"their leaders\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"girlfriends\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the traditional killing of a lion - and exclusion of girls - have been replaced with sporting prowess and increased visibility for women.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the traditional killing\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"a lion\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"exclusion\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting prowess\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"increased visibility\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Events like these are enjoyable because the girls will notice their talent,\\\" said Valentine Naisimoi, still panting after competing in the 100-metre race.\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Events\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 844}, {\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"their talent\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"Valentine Naisimoi\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100-metre race\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Naisimoi explained that many women from her community were expected to fit traditional roles.\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Naisimoi\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"many women\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1028}, {\"ngram\": \"her community\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"traditional roles\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are just there to be married.\\\"\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 19-year-old, whose ambition is to be like famed Kenyan athlete Mary Moraa, said the races gave women like her a moment to shine - and hope for more opportunity.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\", \"score\": 0.9057399212170069, \"rank\": 0.09771087541169547, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_Shelley\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whose ambition\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"the races\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1223}, 