10}, {\"ngram\": \"conservation group\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2133}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The intention was to help preserve the region's lions, which had plummeted from about 30,000 in the 1970s to just over 2,000.\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The intention\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"the region's lions\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1970s\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2260}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The events have helped, according to the Big Life Foundation, with more than 250 lions now roaming the Amboseli ecosystem from fewer than 20 in the early 2000s.\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2323, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Life_Foundation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Big Life Foundation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Life_Foundation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Life_Foundation\"}, {\"begin\": 2385, \"end\": 2393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amboseli_National_Park\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amboseli\", \"types\": [\"Q473972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amboseli_National_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amboseli_National_Park\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The events\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 250 lions\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Runner Stephen Masindet, 21, said the competition was important because it was changing attitudes.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Runner Stephen Masindet\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2493}, {\"ngram\": \"attitudes\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When they see others running, they want to come to train and become champions.\\\"\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2624, \"e